Venezuelan equine encephalomyelitis, Belize
-------------------------------------------
Information received on 08 Oct 2009 from Dr Victor Gongora, Director
of Animal Health, Animal Health Department, Belize Agricultural
Health Authority (BAHA), BELMOPAN, Belize

Summary
Report type: Immediate notification
Start date 25 Jan 2009
Date of 1st confirmation of the event 28 Aug 2009
Report date 08 Oct 2009
Date submitted to OIE 08 Oct 2009
Reason for notification: Reoccurrence of a listed disease
Date of previous occurrence November 2007
Manifestation of disease: Clinical disease
Causal agent: Venezuelan equine encephalomyelitis virus
Nature of diagnosis Clinical, Laboratory (advanced)
This event pertains to the whole country

